+# Phase 2.11 — Routing Incident RCA Usefulness Governor
+
+## Цель
+Построить отдельный usefulness governor именно для `routing incident RCA`, независимо от обычного `operator_rca`.
+
+## Что делает
+- агрегирует `quality_score + usefulness_score`
+- строит decisions по двум скоупам:
+  - `action_pattern = action + prompt_version + policy_version`
+  - `provider_prompt = provider + model_name + prompt_version`
+- выдаёт `SUPPRESS / PROMOTE / HOLD`
+- пишет Redis policy hashes:
+  - `cfg:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_governor:action:*`
+  - `cfg:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_governor:provider:*`
+
+## Smoke checks
+```bash
+redis-cli XREVRANGE stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_governor_decisions + - COUNT 5
+redis-cli XREVRANGE stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_governor_audit + - COUNT 5
+redis-cli HGETALL cfg:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_governor:action:open_incident:routing_incident_rca_v1:policy_v1
+redis-cli HGETALL cfg:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_governor:provider:vertex:gemini-2.5-flash-lite:routing_incident_rca_v1
+curl -s localhost:9889/metrics | grep '^ml_operator_routing_incident_rca_governor_'
+```
+
+## Notes
+- scope только `scanner_infra`
+- advisory-only по умолчанию
+- hot path не затронут
